title: Secret of the Ninja-Choose Your Own Adventure 66.pdf
description:
You're the Star! 29 Exciting Endings!

THE CURSE OF THE NINJA
HAS CAUGHT UP WITH YOU!

You've come to Japan to master the ancient martial art of aikido. One day your friend Nada summons you to her school. She tells you shes being haunted by a terrible curse that began the day an ancient and mysterious sword arrived in the mail. And now the curse is on you, too! To save you both, you must discover the secret of the powerful sword. But how?

If you decide to hunt for the person who sent the sword, turn to page 78. If you decide to go back to the past and find the sword there, turn to page 77. Eut beware the wrath of the ninja! You may wind up drowned in a haunted well or beheaded by a corpse! Or you might break the spell of a vow of revenge that's been spreading evil for a thousand years!

What happens next in the story? lt all depends on the choices you make. How does the story end? Only you can find out! And the best part is that you can keep reading and rereading until you've had not one but many incredibly daring experiences!
